title: (Fri Full Show) Little Big Town in Studio + Is Someone Scamming Bobby? + The Ultimate Fantasy Revenge of a Shady Ex Boyfriend
itunes:title: (Fri Full Show) Little Big Town in Studio + Is Someone Scamming Bobby? + The Ultimate Fantasy Revenge of a Shady Ex Boyfriend
description:
Little Big Town is in studio to discuss their new album that drops today, inspiration behind these songs and why Bobby can't say the name of their new single. Someone oddly texted Bobby's new phone acting as Randy Jackson and Bobby doesn't believe it's him until he gets a phone call. Plus, a caller joins Bobby to discuss her viral story about her friend getting back at her shady ex boyfriend by dropping all of his fantasy football players. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
